Subject: [PATCH 05/18] Add jump detection algorithm for connector
 intersections

- Create jump-calculator.ts with updateConnectorJumps function
- Implement line segment intersection algorithm
- Sort intersections by distance to maintain path order
- Add helper functions: pointToSegmentDistance, findNearestSegment
- Based on draw.io's updateLineJumps (Graph.js:9015-9154)

Phase 3 complete - jump detection ready for rendering integration.

